#.... Read in birds.csv ....
birds <- read.csv("birds.csv")
View(birds)
Code 
#....Isolate Variables with Select().....
birds %>% 
  select(Area, Item, Year, Value) %>% 
  View()

```{r}
#....Isolate Variables with Select().....
birds %>% 
  select(Area, Item, Year, Value) %>% 
  View()

#..... Summary .....
birds %>% 
  select(Area, Item, Year, Value) %>% 
  summary()

unique(birds$Item)

table(birds$Item)
birds %>% 
  select(Area, Item, Year) %>% 
  filter(Item %in% c("Ducks", "Chickens")) %>% 
  table()
```
